CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 14, 1958, pg. B7, reads: "AT TECH - Dale Hubert Bair of Mt. Lebanon, received his Bachelor of Fine Arts in industrial design, and Virginia Mae Ross of Brentwood, won a similar degree in art education also."
TitMainTitle: Graduates, including Dale Hubert Bair and Virginia Mae Ross, recipients of Fine Arts Degrees, at Carnegie Institute of Technology (Carnegie Mellon University) graduation
